name: Blojob
description: BLOJOB is Solana’s most unhinged meme token — built for those who prefer their pumps massive, their dips short, and their liquidity nice and tight. With a legendary 69,000,000,000 supply, BLOJOB is for goons that aren’t afraid to pump their whole load into something. Smooth entry, reckless thrusts toward ATH, and a CumUnity that goes hard until someone blows the charts wide open. Not financial advice — just a very hands-on experience.
